 (1+x)^{1/2}=\sum_{k=0}^\infty\binom{1/2}{k}x^k 
 \begin{align} \binom{1/2}{k} &=\frac{\frac12(\frac12-1)(\frac12-2)\cdots(\frac12-k+1)}{k!}\\ &=\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}{2^kk!}1\cdot3\cdot5\cdots(2k-3)\\ &=\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}{2^kk!}\frac{(2k-2)!}{2^{k-1}(k-1)!}\\ &=\frac{(-1)^{k-1}}{k2^{2k-1}}\binom{2k-2}{k-1} \end{align} 
